For the purposes of section521 of the Act, an entry permit issued on or after 1July 2019must include the following:
(a)the permit holder’s full name;
(b)the name of the organisation that applied for the entry permit;
(c)an expiry date for the entry permit;
(d)a recent photograph of the permit holder that:
(i)shows the holder’s full face; and
(ii)meets requirements that are considered appropriate by the FWC;
(e)the permit holder’s signature.
